text: Grace Tobin (born 9 June 1997) is a New Zealand water polo player. She competed for the New Zealand women's national water polo team in the 2019 World Aquatics Championships. She was educated at Kristin School. == References == == Other websites== * grace-tobin waterpolo.org.nz * waterpolo- champ-heads-spain * women nz Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:New Zealand water polo players
